snippet.title: v5.6 [Elysian Reverie] Trailer - Honkai Impact 3rd
snippet.description:
Honkai Impact 3rd v5.6 [Elysian Reverie] Coming Soon!
New SP Battlesuit [Reverist Calico] debuts!
Elysian Realm major update,
and featured events [Empyrean Legends] and [Starless Night] coming soon! Stay tuned!
